137
00:11:57,239 --> 00:11:58,783
Mi Reuk!

138
00:11:58,897 --> 00:12:00,422
My son!

139
00:12:02,510 --> 00:12:03,620
Mother.

140
00:12:03,323 --> 00:12:05,866
