You must run away.

143
00:12:10,953 --> 00:12:13,463
We heard surveillance is
limited in the upper Amnok.

144
00:12:13,572 --> 00:12:17,599
Cross the river, go to China and
then head for wherever you wish to go.

145
00:12:17,722 --> 00:12:18,658
Mother.

146
00:12:18,785 --> 00:12:20,532
Now.

147
00:12:41,455 --> 00:12:45,099
What... who are you?

148
00:12:50,404 --> 00:12:53,556
You!
What are you...

149
00:13:00,657 --> 00:13:05,240
Did you lure me
here to help them?

150
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:11,876
Our father died because
of those damned Japanese!

151
00:13:11,981 --> 00:13:18,842
How can you work for them?

152
00:13:19,843 --> 00:13:22,931
Surviving made me like this!

153
00:13:23,059 --> 00:13:26,830
I couldn't live, nor
die like a decent person,

154
00:13:26,942 --> 00:13:29,374
so here I am!

155
00:13:30,202 --> 00:13:35,131
I will catch him at all costs!

156
00:13:38,624 --> 00:13:40,124
Orabeoni!!

157
00:13:40,423 --> 00:13:42,823
Orabeoni!

158
00:14:07,126 --> 00:14:09,231
<i>Hurry up.</i>

159
00:14:12,681 --> 00:14:14,753
