Come in.

235
00:22:50,926 --> 00:22:54,177
Brother,
I beg you pardon.

236
00:22:57,045 --> 00:23:00,447
I don't understand this passage.

237
00:23:02,611 --> 00:23:04,111
Is anything wrong?

238
00:23:05,373 --> 00:23:08,445
