00:58:23,663 --> 00:58:28,108
It's an invitation to participate
at our book burning rally next week.

556
00:58:28,295 --> 00:58:30,435
A book burning rally?!

557
00:58:30,436 --> 00:58:36,233
Yes, we will burn all the blasphemous
and detrimental books harming our people.

558
00:58:36,268 --> 00:58:40,418
This will include works by Thomas Mann,
Stefan Zweig, Karl Marx, other Jews...

559
00:58:40,527 --> 00:58:44,550
