563
00:58:57,158 --> 00:58:59,844
Against un-German spirit!

564
00:58:59,960 --> 00:59:02,588
Against un-German spirit!

565
00:59:07,846 --> 00:59:09,520
<i>In the ideological struggle,</i>

566
00:59:10,400 --> 00:59:14,225
<i>books can become
