This is what the great
Chinese philosopher Laozi said.

585
01:01:08,047 --> 01:01:15,733
In Ancient China, Emperor Qin Shi Huang*
burned any scripture trying to criticize him,

586
01:01:08,047 --> 01:01:23,489
{\a6}[*Qin Shi Huang used Fenshu Kengru, a policy to
