588
01:01:24,096 --> 01:01:32,257
But it took nothing more than two
decades for this mighty empire to crumble.

589
01:01:33,436 --> 01:01:36,309
Twenty years is too long.

590
01:01:36,433 --> 01:01:39,317
Even if our scholars end
up perishing to fight Hitler,

591
01:01:39,884 --> 01:01:47,495
wouldn't our resistance against the
Fuhrer shorten that period?

592
01:01:47,630 --> 01:01:54,293
Why should they die?
They will survive and fight instead.

593
01:01:54,758 --> 01:01:59,673
{\a6}[*Huber = famous member of the "White Rose,"
a Nazi resistance group*]

594
01:01:54,758 --> 01:01:57,037
My name is Kurt Huber*.

595
01:01:57,147 --> 01:01:59,673
I'm Mirok Li.

596
01:02:23,026 --> 01:02:25,226
<i>This is my way to help
my beloved Germany, Mirok.</i>

597
01:02:25,355 --> 01:02:27,957
But I hope you'll help
our country in other ways.

598
01:02:28,082 --> 01:02:31,888
<i>It's one of the biggest
publishing houses in Germany.</i>

599
01:02:32,011 --> 01:02:34,040
Would they publish something
from a nameless writer like me,

600
01:02:34,154 --> 01:02:38,523
<i>not to mention someone
from a far away land?</i>

601
01:02:38,710 --> 01:02:42,154
I'm sure they
will publish your work.

602
01:02:42,285 --> 01:02:46,365
<i>Just like your book, "Der Yalu Fliesst,"
will always remain in our memories,</i>

603
01:02:46,478 --> 01:02:49,083
